'''Texas Recreational Road 6''' ('''RE 6''') is a [[List of Texas Recreational Roads|Recreational Road]] located in [[Comanche County, Texas|Comanche County]], in the U.S. state of [[Texas]]. The highway travels from [[Farm to Market Road 1476]] (FM 1476) southward to Sowell Creek Park, on [[Proctor Lake]]. The road is just {{Convert|0.300|mi|km}} long, and connects the park entrance to FM 1476. The highway was designated in 1972, and has never been extended or rerouted. 
[[File:USACE Proctor Lake Texas.jpg|thumb|right|An aerial view of Lake Proctor. RE 6 can be seen in the background]] 

==Route Description==
Recreational Road 6 begins at an intersection with the entrance road to Sowell Creek Park, on [[Lake Proctor]], as a two-lane, paved road. RE 6 travels northward, while Comanche County Road 5132 continues southward. The highway proceeds north, passing a small house to the east. The road passes two large fields to either side, before reaching its northern terminus, an intersection with Farm to Market Road 1476.<ref name="Map 395">{{Texas Mapbook|395|accessdate=June 23, 2012}}</ref><ref name="Lake Proctor Map">{{cite map |cartography=[[U.S. Department of Defense]] |publisher=[[U.S. Army Corps of Engineers]] |url=http://swf67.swf-wc.usace.army.mil/proctor/Information/Maps.asp |title=Proctor Lake Map |accessdate=June 23, 2012}}</ref><ref name="Googlemaps">{{Google Maps|url=https://maps.google.com/maps?f=d&source=s_d&saddr=Co+Rd+432/R+6+Rd&daddr=Co+Rd+432/R+6+Rd&geocode=FX0t6AEdmrIh-g%3BFc4e6AEdMqwh-g&abauth=4fe553beKam7oF8ZShBr2xmEw5c5hn4hQrA&vps=5&ei=GlTlT5PTHoeXsQLk1-HXCQ&jsv=421a&sll=31.993609,-98.455675&sspn=0.005105,0.010568&vpsrc=0&hl=en&mra=ls&num=10|title=Overview Map of Texas Recreational Road 6|accessdate=June 23, 2012}}</ref>

==History==
Recreational Road 6 was designated on October 15, 1972, traveling in its present location from Sowell Creek Park to FM 1476. The highway has not since been extended or rerouted.<ref name="TxDOT"/> RE 6 is currently the shortest route in the Recreational Road System.<ref name="Glossary">{{cite web |author=Staff |publisher=[[Texas Department of Transportation]] |title=Highway Designations Glossary |url=http://www.dot.state.tx.us/business/governments/glossary.htm |accessdate=June 23, 2012}}</ref>

==Major junctions==
This entire route is in [[Comanche County, Texas|Comanche County]].
